; ============================================================================
; Commission — XAUUSD (Gold) — Exness PRO account
; Import: append this line to your run .set, or load alongside it (engine key
;         CommissionPerLot, round-turn USD per 1.0 lot). Symbol specs apply
;         BEFORE load_set, so this value overrides the preset.
; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
; Exness PRO is COMMISSION-FREE — the cost is built into the spread, which the
; tick engine already models from real bid/ask. So the correct value is 0.0.
; Verified 2026-06-16 (Exness Pro = zero commission, spread-based execution).
;
; To switch account type, change the number below (round-turn = per-side x2):
;   PRO         -> 0.0     (commission-free; this file)
;   Raw Spread  -> 7.0     (~$3.50 per lot per side on XAU)
;   Zero        -> 11.0    (~$5.50 per lot per side on XAU)
; ============================================================================
CommissionPerLot=0.0
